'From Squeak3.5 of ''11 April 2003'' [latest update: #5180] on 27 December 2003 at 2:24:57 pm'!"Change Set:		DirEntries-BabelDate:			27 December 2003Author:			Diego Gomez Deck <DiegoGomezDeck@ConsultAr.com>Directory entries names enclosed in _ (underscores) are translatable.This is used in the new Project Repository being developed in Small-Land.  The server simulate some directories to make easier to find a Project.  Directories names like _All_, _By Category_, _By Language_, etc will be displayed in FileList2 translated to the user language.Examples:  '_All_' is shown as 'Todos'  (In Spanish)  '_By Category_' is shown as 'Por Categor’a'  (In Spanish)This method could be used to translate some special folders like Squeaklets, SM, package-cache, etc."!!FileDirectoryWrapper methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'dgd 12/27/2003 14:17'!asString	| result |	result := itemName.	('_*_' match: result)		ifTrue: [result := (result copyFrom: 2 to: result size - 1) translated].	^ result ! !